---
title: Cheesy Corn Fritter & Chicken Tacos with Pico de Gallo, Red Pepper Crema & Scallions
description: You’ll whip up crisp, cheesy corn fritters made with tempura batter, then nestle them in soft, warm flour tortillas for a flavorful new twist on tacos. Top your corn fritter tacos with smoky red pepper crema, juicy pico de gallo, chopped fresh cilantro, and sliced scallions, then brighten it all up with a squeeze of lime juice just before serving.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6643628938584bf020f8c6a1-7495b654.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6644eaeb67f64e4e23f5c457-en-US.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cheesy-corn-fritter-and-chicken-tacos-6644eaeb67f64e4e23f5c457
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Central America
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 1080 kcal
  fat: 46 g
